<HL>
   Troubled Stotler
   Says It Accepts
   Offer From Group
   ----
   By Scott McMurray
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
07/20/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C8
</SO>
